{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "初阳！日出决战 后继有人",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "危急时刻，短暂恢复意识的信玄\\n让幸村知晓了其自身的强大之处。\\n幸村激发了体内申寅两家\\n血统的力量击败信玄，\\n并誓将传承信玄的意志。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "唔……\\n幸儿没法向大帅下手……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110403_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "隐岐",
            "context": "真没劲，你倒是好好打啊，\\n不要一味防守好吗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "出云……\\n你为什么要这么做！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110403_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "隐岐",
            "context": "都说了我不是出云啊。\\n不过我倒是可以回答你这个问题。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110403_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "隐岐",
            "context": "因为我诞生于\\n出云内心的阴影。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "内心的……阴影？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120155_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "侍从长",
            "context": "出云大人，您有向众生传达\\n天照大人圣谕的尊贵使命在身。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110403_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "出云",
            "context": "嗯，我明白。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120155_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "侍从长",
            "context": "如果您的一言一行有失严谨与公正，\\n天照大人的圣谕也自会蒙尘。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110403_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "出云",
            "context": "嗯，我明白。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120155_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "侍从长",
            "context": "为了日出之国，\\n在外请您务必谨言慎行。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110403_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "出云",
            "context": "嗯，我明白。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110403_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "隐岐",
            "context": "出云一直被宫廷的规矩所束缚，\\n为了国家牺牲自由。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110403_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "隐岐",
            "context": "他的痛苦与寂寞\\n在不知不觉中创造了我……\\n所以我非常理解他的感受。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110403_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "隐岐",
            "context": "尤其是他的愤怒……\\n为什么要做出这种\\n牺牲的偏偏是自己。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "唔！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "不行……不能在这里倒下！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110403_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "隐岐",
            "context": "为什么？\\n你不是也被卷入龙氏的斗争\\n而一直被囚禁吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110403_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "隐岐",
            "context": "你明明没有为这个国家而战的理由，\\n却又像这样拼上性命，嘴里说什么\\n决不放弃……简直像个傻子。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "呃啊啊啊！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "唔、唔唔……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110403_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "隐岐",
            "context": "疼吗？难受吗？痛苦吗？\\n好了……赶紧放弃吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "……\\n才不会……放弃呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "幸儿还能……\\n站得起来……还能提得起枪……\\n所以还能继续战斗！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110403_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "隐岐",
            "context": "这就是那什么武士之魂？\\n真是俗不可耐。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110403_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "隐岐",
            "context": "还能站起来是挺了不起……\\n但总是急功近利却空忙活一场的你\\n就算站了起来又有什么意义呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "唔、唔唔……\\n这样下去就要不行了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "（幸儿不想放弃。\\n可是……没有了大帅的\\n幸儿……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "就只是个\\n拖后腿的半吊子……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "不……\\n非也……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "诶？大帅……\\n是大帅吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "别出声……会被那小子发现的，\\n继续假装和老夫战斗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "是、是！哈啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "没错，就是这样……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "大、大帅……\\n您……没事对吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "不……黄泉之气\\n已经游走于老夫全身……\\n老夫能保持清醒的时间应该不长了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "所以你听好了……\\n昨天因为被骸众打断，所以\\n没来得及告诉你……你的强大之处！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "幸儿的……强大之处？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "没错。你常年遭到囚禁，\\n所以不曾拥有身为武士\\n应有的知识和体魄……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "但是你却从未放弃。\\n仅仅为了得到老夫的认可，\\n一次又一次地跌倒再爬起……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "幸儿，这种顽强的生存方式\\n就是你的强大之处。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "大……大帅……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "呵呵……看到你，老夫就会想起\\n年轻时的自己。即使不被父亲看好，\\n也一直坚持修文习武。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "自……己？大帅看见幸儿，\\n会想起自己的过去吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "是啊，你和老夫一样。\\n不……你的顽强比老夫当年\\n是有过之而无不及……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "从父亲手中夺来了家主之位后，\\n面对荒凉的领地上那重重问题之时，\\n即使是老夫也曾数度迷茫并踌躇不前……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "那时，你那爱逞强到不要命的\\n性子虽让老夫很是无奈……\\n但仿佛也鼓舞着老夫。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "幸、幸儿……帮到了\\n信玄大帅吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "嗯……所以，不要去追求什么\\n寅还是申的名头了。\\n你早已继承了老夫顽强的意志……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "非也……是早就超越了老夫。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "你明白自己的强大之处了吧。\\n想必今后也不会再逞莽夫之勇了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "所以……斩了老夫吧。\\n跨过这具尸体……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "你也还能继续战斗对吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "大帅……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110403_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "隐岐",
            "context": "这士兵的动作怎么这么迟钝呢？\\n真没劲。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110403_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "隐岐",
            "context": "对了，那就稍微增加一些\\n黄泉之气吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "呃……唔！？\\n黄泉之气又……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "大帅！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "唔、唔……\\n唔啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "大帅！？大帅！\\n呃啊啊！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "唔、唔唔……\\n大……帅……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "大帅……\\n幸儿真是傻啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "明明继承寅之龙氏并不是\\n继承大帅衣钵的唯一方法……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "明明大帅早就认可了幸儿的\\n内在……幸儿却浑然不知……\\n一直在做着无用功……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "不行……不能哭，\\n幸儿的强项就是顽强，\\n无论何时都不会倒下——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110403_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "隐岐",
            "context": "什么！为什么你挨了那么多\\n攻击还能站起来！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0068",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "我也不知道为什么……\\n只是，幸儿还能站得起来，\\n还能提得起枪，自然也就……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_06_0069",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
